'''法羅群島國教會'''（Fólkakirkjan）是世界規模最小的一個[[國教會|國教會]]之一<ref>Referenced at the Encyclopedia of Global Religion, edited by Mark Juergensmeyer, published 2012 by Sage publications, ISBN 978-0-7619-2729-7, page 390. (Page available on-line [https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=WwJzAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA390&lpg=PA390&dq=faroe+islands+state+church&source=bl&ots=WqblMGRHqp&sig=BC0o4LtuKwp89TZnv91btuvgMsY&hl=en&sa=X&ei=1lnyVK21B8atU5CkgJgL&ved=0CD4Q6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=faroe%20islands%20state%20church&f=false here] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=WwJzAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA390&lpg=PA390&dq=faroe+islands+state+church&source=bl&ots=WqblMGRHqp&sig=BC0o4LtuKwp89TZnv91btuvgMsY&hl=en&sa=X&ei=1lnyVK21B8atU5CkgJgL&ved=0CD4Q6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=faroe%20islands%20state%20church&f=false |date=20190603100028 }}).</ref>。在2007年7月29日之前，法羅群島教會是[[信義宗|信義宗]][[丹麥教會|丹麥教會]]的下屬教區之一。法羅群島83%的人口是法羅群島教會的信徒<ref>http://www.folkakirkjan.fo/default.aspx?pageid=6235&sectionid=207 {{Wayback|url=http://www.folkakirkjan.fo/default.aspx?pageid=6235&sectionid=207 |date=20150308090058 }} Fólkakirkjan's official website (in Faroese)</ref>。
== 现任领导人 ==
现任的主教（首席牧师）是 Jógvan Fríðriksson牧师<ref>See his directory entry and photograph on the [http://www.folkakirkjan.fo/Default.aspx?pageid=6484 official website] {{Wayback|url=http://www.folkakirkjan.fo/Default.aspx?pageid=6484 |date=20171117102432 }} of the Church.</ref>。教务长是受人尊敬的Naes牧师。 从古至今，都保持有大约二十五名牧师为法罗群岛教会的教会服务。
